These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-1::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, watermelon, radish, eggplant, onion, lettuce
1. the person eating watermelon is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
3. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
4. the person eating apple is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
5. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating apple and the person eating lettuce##2
8. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |      4       |   5    |   6   |
| Food   | onion | watermelon | lettuce | eggplant | apple | radish |

