.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, handball, surfing, climbing, soccer, parkour
1. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
2. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |  3   |    4     |   5    |   6   |
| Sport   | volleyball | climbing | handball | surfing | soccer | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-3::.
