1. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing go##8
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |   3   |     4      |  5  |   6    |
| Game   | chess | monopoly | canasta | scrabble | go | backgammon |

