.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-8-5::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, almond-milk, lemonade, coffee, sprite
 1. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
 6. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##7
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 9. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |    4     |   5   |       6       |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta | almond-milk | tea | lemonade | coffee |

