4. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
7. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
8. the person who likes azure is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes turquise##7

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |   2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |  6  |
| Color   | coral | apricot | azure | turquise | pink | light-blue |

