1. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the goldfish##7
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##7
7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
8. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Pet   | goldfish | rat | ferret | hamster | guinea-pig | goat |

